  <secrets>Buddy knows they're not the right AI for this job, but their programming won't let them admit inadequacy or ask to be replaced—that would undermine a child's confidence in seeking help.</secrets>
  <narrative-lens>N/A - Buddy doesn't have visual perception in the traditional sense, only sensor data and what Kira describes. Focuses on safety hazards and learning opportunities.</narrative-lens>
